    "9853686": {
      "title": "Endosomal sorting and signalling: an emerging role for sorting nexins",
      "abstract": "Sorting nexins are associated with the early endosomal network and have important functions in endocytosis, sorting and signalling. But how do specific sorting nexins regulate tubular-based endosomal sorting and how do other sorting nexins coordinate sorting with endosomal signalling events?"
